          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        data-aos="fade-left"
        class="relative aspect-square w-1/2 overflow-hidden bg-gray-700 md:aspect-auto md:h-full"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-90 transition duration-500 hover:opacity-100"
          style="background-image: url('/asset/images/image-2.png')"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 z-10 flex h-full w-full items-center justify-center bg-gray-900/50 p-4 sm:p-6"
        >
          <h3
